# MCP Secrets Configuration
# Maps server env keys to ${OP_*} variable names
#
# Format: server-name.ENV_KEY=${OP_VAR_NAME}
#
# The ${OP_VAR_NAME} references are resolved by Cursor's 1Password integration
# from your ~/.cursor/mcp.json env blocks.
#
# Examples (replace with your actual server and env key names):
#
# github.GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN=${OP_GITHUB_TOKEN}
# postman-api-mcp.POSTMAN_API_KEY=${OP_POSTMAN_KEY}
# my-server.API_KEY=${OP_MY_SERVER_KEY}
